{"tid":687541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實台灣人都幾撚可悲 有時候真係仲覺得差過大陸人","createTime":"2018-06-02T11:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T06:43:20.000Z","uid":184570,"like":21,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4dfa479182ab5a1b407bd0c3e81506006287556e","tid":687541,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"個人覺得 台灣真係同大陸既人質素真係無咩分別 <br />\n<br />\n仲成撚日講9人地質素有幾差 根本就50步笑100步<br />\n<br />\n同大陸人一樣 成日以為自己有幾清高 有幾高上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無知又唔認 成撚日用台灣既濕9法律想告其他國家既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日笑9大陸人玻璃心 根本自己咪又係一撚樣 <br />\n<br />\n有時打機聽到台灣人講Taiwan NO.1 仲意為好撚型 比鬼佬笑緊都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要有時話9香港人係大陸人 ,我真係笑而不語 根本如果咁講你地d台灣狗咪又係大陸人 知道歷史都知 以前既台灣人咪姐係大陸人 真係好撚無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係個句 我屌臭你啦 台灣狗畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9da7e7cb744842b04add3655ee856583903f410","tid":687541,"uid":124283,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"呢段野 Apply 落香港人度都得"},{"pid":"1e0935509c3e75ef2e3e086358d2013e5a221e27","tid":687541,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c9da7e7cb744842b04add3655ee856583903f410","tid":687541,"uid":124283,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"呢段野 Apply 落香港人度都得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff275f80ea5e4cb581814cd0512d95657268cffc","tid":687541,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"利申 唔係支持大陸 唔記得左打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a6463166da488ca55b5c67b9f44d3e7584bcda","tid":687541,"uid":44454,"like":3,"